AKS was supported by the Searle Scholars Program, the Beckman Young Investigator Program, the Pew-Stewart Scholars Program for Cancer Research, a Sloan Fellowship in Chemistry, the NIH (1U54CA217377, 2P01AI039671, 5U24AI118672, 1U2CCA23319501) and the Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation. PKB and SLC were supported by the NIH (5R01CA227156-02, 1R21CA220253-0A01 and 1R01CA244975-01). PKB was also supported by Susan G. Komen. SLC was also supported by the Wong Family Award, the DF/HCC Lung Cancer Program Developmental Research Project Award in Lung Cancer Research, and by Dana-Farber Institutional Research Support. DPC was supported by the Tawingo Fund. CAA was supported by an NIH/NINDS R25, the American Brain Tumor Association, and AANS/CNS Joint Section on Tumors.
